---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Mi Espacio | Marcelo">
  <main class="container">
    
    <!-- Hero Header -->
    <header class="hero">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <!-- Monospace Code tag instead of standard developer subtitles -->
        <span class="code-tag">
          &lt;<span class="code-keyword">import</span> <span class="code-function">Marcelo</span> <span class="code-keyword">from</span> <span class="code-string">'life'</span> /&gt;
        </span>
        <h1>¡Hi! Soy Marcelo.</h1>
        <p class="hero-description">
          Qué bueno tenerte por acá. Te cuento un poco sobre mí: me apasiona buscar la velocidad y la concentración en todo lo que hago. Ya sea sentado frente a la pantalla resolviendo algoritmos, rodando al máximo en la ruta, buscando silencio bajo el agua o desafiando al reloj con mis cubos, siempre busco llevar la mente y el cuerpo al límite.
        </p>
        
        <div class="hero-stats">
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="code-comment">// Speedcubing</span>
            <span class="stat-num">*3x3</span>
            <span class="stat-lbl">*2x2</span>
            <span class="stat-lbl">*piramix</span>
            <span class="stat-lbl">*mirror</span>
            <span class="stat-lbl">*tower cube</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="code-comment">// ciclismo_estilo</span>
            <span class="stat-num">Vel. & Resistencia</span>
            <span class="stat-lbl">Velocidad</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="code-comment">// natacion_core</span>
            <span class="stat-num">Resistencia</span>
            <span class="stat-lbl">Brazada</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="code-comment">// others</span>
            <span class="stat-lbl">*Wally</span>
            <span class="stat-lbl">*Futsal</span>
            <span class="stat-lbl">*Star Craft</span>
            <span class="stat-lbl">*CTR(Pro)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Rotating Circle Profile Frame -->
      <div class="profile-avatar-container">
        <div class="profile-avatar-glow"></div>
        <div class="profile-avatar-img">
          <img src="/me/profile.jpeg" alt="Foto de perfil" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Sections Title -->
    <div class="section-title-wrap">
      <span class="code-comment">/* function getDisciplinas() &#123; return [ciclismo, natacion, cubos]; &#125; */</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Lo que define my week</h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Passions Grid -->
    <section class="sections-grid">
      
      <!-- Cycling Card -->
      <article class="glass-panel cycling-panel">
        <span class="code-comment">// const bici = &#123; estilo: 'velocidad', terreno: 'ruta' &#125;;</span>
        <div class="card-icon cycling-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="5.5" cy="17.5" r="2.5"></circle>
            <circle cx="18.5" cy="17.5" r="2.5"></circle>
            <path d="M15 6h5v2h-5z"></path>
            <path d="M12 17.5V14l-3-3 4-3 2 3h2"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Adrenalina</h3>
        <p class="hero-description" style="margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">
          Me encanta salir a correr buscando velocidad o subiendo aceras (no importa si es la bici de carrera, le meto no mas). Me encanta cuando pasa una moto y trato de pasarlo, pues no pasa pero lo intento. XD
        </p>
        <div class="card-img-container" style="margin-top: 1.2rem;">
          <img src="/me/cycling.png" alt="Mi bicicleta de carretera" />
        </div>
        <div class="metrics">
          <div>
            <div class="metric-bar-label">
              <span class="code-tag cyan">bici.velocidad</span>
              <span>90%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric-bar-bg">
              <div class="metric-bar-fill" style="width: 90%; background-color: var(--accent-cyan);"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="metric-bar-label">
              <span class="code-tag cyan">bici.control_curvas</span>
              <span>85%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric-bar-bg">
              <div class="metric-bar-fill" style="width: 85%; background-color: var(--accent-cyan);"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Swimming Card -->
      <article class="glass-panel swimming-panel">
        <span class="code-comment">// function meditar(piscina) &#123; return silencio; &#125;</span>
        <div class="card-icon swimming-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M2 6c.6.5 1.2 1 2.5 1C5.8 7 7 6 8.5 6c1.5 0 2.7 1 4 1 1.3 0 2.5-1 4-1 1.5 0 2.7 1 4 1 1.3 0 2.5-1 4-1"></path>
            <path d="M2 12c.6.5 1.2 1 2.5 1C5.8 13 7 12 8.5 12c1.5 0 2.7 1 4 1 1.3 0 2.5-1 4-1 1.5 0 2.7 1 4 1 1.3 0 2.5-1 4-1"></path>
            <path d="M2 18c.6.5 1.2 1 2.5 1C5.8 19 7 18 8.5 18c1.5 0 2.7 1 4 1 1.3 0 2.5-1 4-1 1.5 0 2.7 1 4 1 1.3 0 2.5-1 4-1"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Nadar a mi ritmo</h3>
        <p class="hero-description" style="margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">
          Me encanta ir a la piscina, ya sea capachos, o la piscina olimpica, es sin duda lo mejor del dia, pasaría todo el día ahi pero saldria muy remojado, cierto también hay que trabajar.
        </p>
        <div class="card-img-container" style="margin-top: 1.2rem;">
          <img src="/me/swimming.png" alt="Nadando en la piscina" />
        </div>
        <div class="metrics">
          <div>
            <div class="metric-bar-label">
              <span class="code-tag blue">natacion.resistencia</span>
              <span>80%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric-bar-bg">
              <div class="metric-bar-fill" style="width: 80%; background-color: #3b82f6;"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="metric-bar-label">
              <span class="code-tag blue">natacion.crol_tecnica</span>
              <span>75%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric-bar-bg">
              <div class="metric-bar-fill" style="width: 75%; background-color: #3b82f6;"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Speedcubing Card -->
      <article class="glass-panel speedcube-panel">
        <span class="code-comment">// class Speedcuber extends Mindset &#123;&#125;</span>
        <div class="card-icon cube-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
            <line x1="9" y1="3" x2="9" y2="21"></line>
            <line x1="15" y1="3" x2="15" y2="21"></line>
            <line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"></line>
            <line x1="3" y1="15" x2="21" y2="15"></line>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Desafíos en tres dimensiones</h3>
        <p class="hero-description" style="margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">
          Soy algo nuevo en Sppedcubing ya que lo adopte como miniterapia al momento de trabajar mientras analizo y para no ver el celular, pero con el tiempo fui practicando y si, me considero un SpeedCuber por que ahora practico para mejorar mis marcas.
          Dejare esto por aquí (L' B L' 2F L B' L' 2F 2L U')
        </p>
        
        <!-- Interactive 3D CSS Cube -->
        <div class="cube-3d-wrap">
          <div class="cube-3d">
            <!-- Front Face -->
            <div class="cube-face face-front">
              <div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div>
              <div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div>
              <div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div>
            </div>
            <!-- Back Face -->
            <div class="cube-face face-back">
              <div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div>
              <div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div>
              <div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div>
            </div>
            <!-- Left Face -->
            <div class="cube-face face-left">
              <div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div>
              <div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div>
              <div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div>
            </div>
            <!-- Right Face -->
            <div class="cube-face face-right">
              <div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div>
              <div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div>
              <div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div>
            </div>
            <!-- Top Face -->
            <div class="cube-face face-top">
              <div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div>
              <div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div>
              <div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div>
            </div>
            <!-- Bottom Face -->
            <div class="cube-face face-bottom">
              <div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div>
              <div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div>
              <div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div><div class="cube-sticker"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Master Project Card -->
      <article class="glass-panel master-panel">
        <span class="code-comment">// TODO: findMasterProject();</span>
        <div class="card-icon master-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22" height="22" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polygon points="12 2 2 7 12 12 22 7 12 2"></polygon>
            <polyline points="2 17 12 22 22 17"></polyline>
            <polyline points="2 12 12 17 22 12"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>El gran enigma: Mi Proyecto Maestro</h3>
        <p class="hero-description" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
          Sigo buscando mi proyecto maestro. Ese gran desarrollo técnico que logre unir todo lo que me vuela la cabeza: la simulación interactiva, los algoritmos avanzados y la visualización de datos. Todavía no está listo, pero sigo construyendo prototipos, jugando con código y buscando esa gran idea.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Tech Terminal Mockup -->
        <div class="terminal">
          <div class="terminal-header">
            <div class="terminal-dots">
              <span class="terminal-dot dot-red"></span>
              <span class="terminal-dot dot-yellow"></span>
              <span class="terminal-dot dot-green"></span>
            </div>
            <span class="terminal-title">master_scanner_engine.log</span>
          </div>
          <div class="terminal-body">
            <div class="term-line">
              <span class="term-cmd">marcelo@desktop:~$</span>
              <span class="term-txt">./scan_master_projects.sh</span>
            </div>
            <div class="term-line">
              <span class="term-cmd">[STATUS]</span>
              <span>Analyzing stack ideas (WebGL, Node, Go, Rust, AI)...</span>
            </div>
            <div class="term-line">
              <span class="term-cmd">[INFO]</span>
              <span>Potential candidates: IoT Telemetry Dashboard, 3D Warehouse Engine...</span>
            </div>
            <div class="term-line">
              <span class="term-cmd">[WARN]</span>
              <span>Core project fit: STILL_IN_DEVELOPMENT</span>
            </div>
            <div class="term-line">
              <span class="term-cmd">[ACTION]</span>
              <span>Continue exploring, coding, and building...</span>
            </div>
            <div class="term-progress-wrap">
              <span>Progreso:</span>
              <div class="term-progress-bar">
                <div class="term-progress-fill"></div>
              </div>
              <span class="term-val">45% COMPLETADO</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

    </section>

    <!-- Mosaic Gallery Title -->
    <div class="section-title-wrap" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <span class="code-comment">/* function renderGallery() &#123; return images; &#125; */</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Momentos en Imágenes</h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Gallery Grid -->
    <section class="mosaic-section">
      <div class="mosaic-grid">
        
        <div class="mosaic-card">
          <img src="/me/profile.jpeg" alt="Perfil" />
          <div class="mosaic-overlay">
            <span class="code-tag emerald">[const self]</span>
            <span class="mosaic-title">Me</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mosaic-card">
          <img src="/me/bici.jpeg" alt="Ciclismo" />
          <div class="mosaic-overlay">
            <span class="code-tag cyan">[const speed]</span>
            <span class="mosaic-title">Mi bicicleta</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mosaic-card placeholder-card">
          <div class="placeholder-content">
            <span class="code-comment">// 404: img_not_found</span>
            <span class="code-tag amber">awaiting_upload()</span>
            <p>Muy pronto...</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mosaic-overlay">
            <span class="code-tag blue">[const flow]</span>
            <span class="mosaic-title">Sesión en Piscina</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mosaic-card">
          <img src="/me/cubes.png" alt="Colección de cubos" />
          <div class="mosaic-overlay">
            <span class="code-tag amber">[const algorithms]</span>
            <span class="mosaic-title">Mi Desk de Speedcubing</span>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="db-footer">
      <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Marcelo.</p>
    </footer>

  </main>
</Layout>
